            <h1>What is this?</h1>
            <p>Simply put, ColorExplorer is an online toolbox for working with color palettes. Being a little more elaborate, the current site is the result of evolvement on my acclaimed <a href="http://www.colormatch5k.com" target="_blank">ColorMatch 5K</a> project dating back as far as 2001.</p>
            <p>With ColorExplorer you can quickly and easily create, manage and evaluate color palettes for use in graphic design, web designs, layouts, and much more.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="width:280px;float:left;margin-right:15px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;">
