            <p>Registering for a free user profile, however, will give you a few extras (e.g. better and safer palette control/access).</p>
            <p>You may also opt for a paid registration to get unlimited number of palettes to save but most important of all; to support this free project! <a href="userprofile.aspx">Read more ...</a></p>
        </div>
        <div style="width:280px;float:left;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;">
